  "text": "We included data from all hornets, including those that did not exhibit any learning. We ran separate analyses for learning and memory, using the PER score and the discrimination index (DI, the response to the CS minus the response to the unrewarded, novel control odour) [CITATION_1] . At each test time point per hornet, the DI has a potential value of −1, 0 or 1.",
